      <title>泰国意外降息凸显亚洲经济增长忧虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/surprise-thai-rate-cut-highlights-growth-worries-across-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行意外放弃了长期以来抵制降息的态度，凸显出人们对东南亚经济增长的担忧日益超过通胀风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/surprise-thai-rate-cut-highlights-growth-worries-across-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 08:47:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度 9 月贸易逆差因黄金进口放缓而缩小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/india-s-september-trade-gap-narrows-as-import-bill-declines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于黄金进口量放缓导致印度进口费用下降，9 月份印度贸易逆差收窄至五个月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/india-s-september-trade-gap-narrows-as-import-bill-declines</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 08:47:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rightmove 称英国房东正在以创纪录的速度出售房屋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/uk-landlords-are-selling-up-at-a-record-pace-rightmove-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心更严格的绿色规则以及即将到来的预算中税收增加的前景，英国买房出租的房东正在以创纪录的数量出售房屋，这给租户带来了进一步的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/uk-landlords-are-selling-up-at-a-record-pace-rightmove-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因盈利疲软而下跌；英镑下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于奢侈品行业盈利疲软，半导体行业盈利前景不容乐观，欧洲股市下跌。英国通胀率下降，刺激市场对降息的预期增强，英镑下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 22:06:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利将利用银行、保险公司提供 35 亿欧元预算计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/italy-to-tap-banks-insurers-for-3-5-billion-deputy-pm-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治娅·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 的内阁正在寻求意大利银行和保险公司的帮助，为其预算提供 35 亿欧元（38 亿美元）的资金，这是一项旨在兑现向选民承诺的新计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/italy-to-tap-banks-insurers-for-3-5-billion-deputy-pm-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 19:58:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士河危机后，英国监管机构考虑提高投资者回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/uk-regulator-weighs-higher-investor-returns-as-thames-woes-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司危机推高了整个行业的借贷成本后，英国水务监管机构首次考虑提高投资者的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/uk-regulator-weighs-higher-investor-returns-as-thames-woes-bite</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 18:44:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
